metadata.name: Toadeez #1
metadata.description: Toadeez is a fun and cute collection of pixelated toads in various colors, sizes, and poses. Each toad is a unique Non-Fungible Token (NFT) that can be bought and sold in a digital marketplace. The toads can be collected and used as decorations, digital art, and even virtual pets. Each toad has its own personality and characteristics, making it a great way to share your love of toads with the world. The collection also includes rare and limited edition toads that can be collected for extra value. With Toadeez, you can bring a touch of cuteness and fun to your digital life! Full cc0, free degen mint, derivative of multiple projects.
